# Print iio analog reading each second
# iio_device: will first try any device whose name is 'adc1x8s102'. If fails,
# will try to create it using the 'create' command. If it fails, tries
# IIO device whose id is '0'.

adc(MyADC)
timer(timer)

timer OUT -> TICK adc OUT -> IN _(console)
